{"tid":1668452,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"傳謝振中最快下月調離警察公共關係科","createTime":"2019-10-22T03:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-22T08:43:42.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"348cb88cbedcc227b40dc43524b6b9112a16e39f","tid":1668452,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T03:56:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://news.memehk.com/img/post/20926_221019a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F20926_221019a.jpg&h=a34836ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多月來警察4時召開的記者會，均由警察公共關係科（PPRB）總警司謝振中主持，不過最近有消息指，謝sir最快會在下月開始調離警察公共關係科。<br />\n<br />\n剛放完兩星期大假的謝sir昨日回歸記者會，不過多次在警方例行記者會上為警隊護航的謝sir除傳出妻兒正申請美國綠卡外，亦有消息指他會最快在下月調職離開警察公共關係科，轉往負責遴選同袍升職。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://news.memehk.com/posts/20926</code></pre>"},{"pid":"2b3ffeca4b599bcfc6a306016b18d21dc18c97f6","tid":1668452,"uid":126283,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:00:51.000Z","msg":"被猜忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8032fc827b4e3071a446a7d3a84a0dcc8cbafd8f","tid":1668452,"uid":9315,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"2b3ffeca4b599bcfc6a306016b18d21dc18c97f6","tid":1668452,"uid":126283,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:00:51.000Z","msg":"被猜忌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T04:04:06.000Z","msg":"保得住張綠卡嘅話比班狗猜忌下又有乜所謂<br />\n人地就去大灣區  佢就去美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b0307bab10ebdc25f14a943acf4995886c08aa","tid":1668452,"uid":10064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-